### health
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/health

### device
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/device

### create session
POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/session
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "site_name": "HAMADYA",
  "part_name": "1.1.3.2",
  "module_part_number": "TWMND-72HD580",
  "operator": "tech-1"
}

### update metadata
POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/session/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/metadata
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "site_name": "HAMADYA",
  "part_name": "1.1.3.3"
}

### trigger measure
POST http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/session/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/measure

### get session result
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/session/REPLACE_SESSION_ID/result

### list results
GET http://127.0.0.1:8765/api/results
